103
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:33,300
You're a lot shorter than me.

104
00:08:52,570 --> 00:08:54,430
Cheers!

105
00:08:59,010 --> 00:09:02,880
Uncaring punk, how could you not even call me once?

106
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:07,060
Why? Were you going to get married while I wasn't around?

107
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:10,140
It was lonely without you around.

108
00:09:10,140 --> 00:09:12,660
That's why you should start dating someone.

109
00:09:12,660 --> 00:09:14,520
Really though.

110
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:17,400
