112
00:09:20,380 --> 00:09:24,360
Hey! You should be the one giving presents.

113
00:09:27,350 --> 00:09:31,990
What the heck? Did you really buy this?

114
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:36,890
That is the one you are using, right? You were almost out.

115
00:09:39,310 --> 00:09:42,450
Aigoo, this innocent punk.

116
00:09:44,470 --> 00:09:47,290
What did you think about while you were in Santiago?

117
00:09:52,730 --> 00:09:58,320
What I should throw away from my life, and what I should take. Those kinds of thoughts.

118
00:09:58,320 --> 00:10:02,340
Ohhh. Then what's the result?

119
00:10:03,180 --> 00:10:05,300
Firstly, you.

120
00:10:06,190 --> 00:10:08,800
Let's take this off and then talk. It's so suffocating.

121
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:12,190
Ehhh.

122
00:10:12,190 --> 00:10:14,190
Let me take it off.

123
00:10:14,190 --> 00:10:15,400
Just five more minutes.

124
00:10:27,970 --> 00:10:38,230
