Did your friends' wedding yesterday go well?

138
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:36,900
- Yeah.
- You don't regret not taking me?

139
00:11:36,900 --> 00:11:39,490
Uh, you don't really know my friends.

140
00:11:39,490 --> 00:11:41,660
You'll probably come to regret it.

141
00:11:52,070 --> 00:11:56,080
I'm not ready. You came early.

142
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:59,890
It's nice working with you. I can see you any time,

143
00:11:59,890 --> 00:12:02,220
