144
00:12:02,220 --> 00:12:07,140
I think like this when you are busy explaining things to me. Ah...

145
00:12:07,140 --> 00:12:09,670
I want to make her work hard.

146
00:12:10,660 --> 00:12:12,190
Concentrate on your work.

147
00:12:12,190 --> 00:12:16,610
You think I would just work with you? Nonsense!

148
00:12:17,290 --> 00:12:20,810
