- Exactly!

149
00:12:20,810 --> 00:12:25,990
First off, with the charity and  autograph events you did so far,

150
00:12:25,990 --> 00:12:28,050
I made a first draft of the story for the advertisement.

151
00:12:28,050 --> 00:12:33,170
During a performance, heavily armed with both charms and spunk.

152
00:12:33,170 --> 00:12:36,990
But, you probably won't find him in a gym.

153
00:12:36,990 --> 00:12:41,830
The different charisma of Cha Seo Woo when he smiles brightly and talks loudly.

154
00:12:41,830 --> 00:12:46,440
The aura of innocence despite being not so young.

155
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:53,330
An intimacy, like family or a sibling... Like a friend.

156
00:12:53,330 --> 00:12:57,290
Everything is like one—

157
00:12:58,850 --> 00:13:01,600
A different look to Choi Won.

158
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:05,250
Picture of Choi Won on the company publication.

159
00:13:05,250 --> 00:13:08,760
Awesome, I am going to tease him totally.

160
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:13,000
Why are you laughing? Who are you talking to?

161
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:15,500
- It's nothing.
- A friend.

162
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:17,900
Yeah, Na Yeong.

163
00:13:17,900 --> 00:13:20,110
Call that friend to eat with us later.

164
00:13:20,110 --> 00:13:21,620
Why?

165
00:13:21,620 --> 00:13:24,810
I need to know why you're laughing.

166
00:13:24,810 --> 00:13:27,800
You're curious about everything.

167
00:13:27,800 --> 00:13:30,040
Let's  continue.

168
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:36,210
Alright!  Toast to the best crew member!

169
00:13:36,210 --> 00:13:41,090
- Cheers!
- Congrats!

170
00:13:43,510 --> 00:13:46,300
Sunbae, how does it feel to be chosen as the best flight attendant?

171
00:13:46,300 --> 00:13:50,960
Indeed, the customers' perception is accurate!

172
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:54,030
- What?
- Watching how he keeps getting chosen,

173
00:13:54,030 --> 00:13:55,640
I think there's a problem with the selection process.

174
00:13:55,640 --> 00:13:59,590
There's a huge problem! You can just see that after I got eliminated!

175
00:13:59,590 --> 00:14:01,860
That one is quite an accurate decision.

176
00:14:01,860 --> 00:14:05,650
I really want to be chosen once. How do you it? What's the method?

177
00:14:05,650 --> 00:14:06,990
- Method?
- Yes.

178
00:14:06,990 --> 00:14:10,440
Listen well. First.

179
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:12,490
Looks?

180
00:14:14,230 --> 00:14:18,190
Looks!

181
00:14:21,330 --> 00:14:31,600
♬  I want to see you. I want to see you ♬

182
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:36,980
♬  To the point you start hating me  ♬

183
00:14:36,980 --> 00:14:42,870
Aigoo, you're something else, Choi Won. You're already drunk.

184
00:14:42,870 --> 00:14:44,920
Sunbae.

185
00:14:44,920 --> 00:14:52,180
♬  To the point you start hating me  ♬

186
00:14:53,360 --> 00:15:03,560
♬  I want to see you. I want to see you  ♬

187
00:15:03,560 --> 00:15:11,650
♬  To the point you start hating me  ♬

188
