Jumei has a lot of interest in the ChaAndy project.

196
00:17:38,690 --> 00:17:42,690
It would be nice for you to go to the main office in China, too.

197
00:17:42,690 --> 00:17:47,430
Wherever and whatever it is, I'm okay with it if I'm with you.

198
00:17:49,880 --> 00:17:53,180
Don't answer any phone calls when you're with me.

199
00:17:53,180 --> 00:17:56,000
I don't want to be interrupted when I'm with you.

200
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:11,000
The person you have dialed is unavailable. Please leave a message after the beep.

201
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:15,640
What time is it right now that she'd not be answering her phone?

202
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:18,820
She is quite suspicious these days.

203
00:18:18,820 --> 00:18:21,080
You're worrying about useless things again.

204
00:18:21,080 --> 00:18:25,950
What if she's meeting some strange man again?

205
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:41,890
Team Leader.

206
00:18:42,860 --> 00:18:46,620
What? These people who didn't even support the project, seriously.

207
00:18:46,620 --> 00:18:51,600
