210
00:18:58,360 --> 00:19:01,260
They really have no conscience.

211
00:19:01,260 --> 00:19:05,590
Thanks, Minji. I'll take care of everything, so you don't have to worry about it.

212
00:19:05,590 --> 00:19:07,250
Yes.

213
00:19:17,770 --> 00:19:21,390
Design team. Let me know everything before you proceed with anything.

214
