215
00:19:22,710 --> 00:19:25,850
Because the ChaAndy collaboration's concept, story, and promotion...

216
00:19:25,850 --> 00:19:29,580
You should know that I'm the one who handled everything, right?

217
00:19:29,580 --> 00:19:33,700
