231
00:20:43,740 --> 00:20:48,630
Will it be cleanly wrapped up? What if it's going to tie you even more to them?

232
00:20:48,630 --> 00:20:50,580
I'll think about it.

233
00:21:02,500 --> 00:21:07,440
Your first visit on this hands-on-training program is the reservation center.

234
00:21:07,440 --> 00:21:09,350
This reservation center operates 24 hours.

235
00:21:09,350 --> 00:21:12,360
Employees in the Americas, or the telecommuters, will answer the phones at night

236
00:21:12,360 --> 00:21:14,410
to reduce customer inconvenience.

237
00:21:14,410 --> 00:21:17,870
This is the same model that is used in the planes.

238
00:21:17,870 --> 00:21:21,840
The attendants who announce on the planes have received the highest score during their training.

239
00:21:21,840 --> 00:21:24,000
Like Sunbae?

240
00:21:25,700 --> 00:21:28,570
Do you mind if we take a photo, Sunbae?

241
00:21:28,570 --> 00:21:32,620
Please, please, please!

242
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:39,770
One, two...

243
00:21:41,600 --> 00:21:44,030
Take mine too.

244
00:21:44,800 --> 00:21:47,400
One, two, three...

