253
00:22:38,340 --> 00:22:41,380
even as a friend, then

254
00:22:41,380 --> 00:22:43,340
I want to do it too.

255
00:22:43,340 --> 00:22:47,740
Staying next to you as a hoobae (junior),

256
00:22:47,740 --> 00:22:50,390
please let me at least do that.

257
00:22:51,700 --> 00:22:55,750
Lee So Eun, don't do things like that.

258
00:23:16,400 --> 00:23:18,360
Sold out

259
00:23:30,000 --> 00:23:33,970
Looking at you circling around with the empty cart,

260
00:23:33,970 --> 00:23:36,990
what is it? What happened?

261
00:23:36,990 --> 00:23:39,480
Nothing. It's nothing.

262
00:23:39,480 --> 00:23:42,360
Is that right? Then alright.

263
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:46,810
You bought a lot? What did you buy?

264
00:23:46,810 --> 00:23:50,770
Don't covet someone else's cart. There is nothing to eat at home.

265
00:23:50,770 --> 00:23:52,790
Us too.

266
00:23:52,790 --> 00:23:54,860
Uh? This is?...

267
00:23:54,860 --> 00:23:57,420
I wanted to buy it but they were all sold out.

268
00:23:57,420 --> 00:23:59,590
I took what was left.

269
00:23:59,590 --> 00:24:03,140
Hey! Give it back.

270
00:24:04,100 --> 00:24:05,370
Let's maintain proper distance.

271
00:24:05,370 --> 00:24:07,640
Okay, okay.

272
00:24:07,640 --> 00:24:11,580
I'll concede to you. But give up the wine.

273
00:24:12,900 --> 00:24:17,230
Hey! Hey! Ah, wait, wait...

274
00:24:26,500 --> 00:24:28,190
Uhm this is nice.

275
00:24:28,190 --> 00:24:30,940
Hmm, right.

276
00:24:37,300 --> 00:24:38,840
Things going well?

277
00:24:38,840 --> 00:24:40,460
Of course.

278
00:24:40,460 --> 00:24:43,260
Indeed you are Team Leader Oh Ha Na.

279
00:24:43,260 --> 00:24:45,820
So you were doing well as usual.

280
00:24:51,500 --> 00:24:56,560
What is it? Did Team Leader Oh get stabbed in the back again?

281
00:24:57,560 --> 00:25:01,950
There you go again. Looking at things haphazardly. I am Oh Ha Na, you know.

282
00:25:05,300 --> 00:25:08,550
Everything is going well with Cha Seo Hoo, right?

283
00:25:08,550 --> 00:25:14,470
Of course! Being with you like this, makes me want some chicken feet.

284
00:25:14,470 --> 00:25:16,850
Is that all you think about when you see me?

285
00:25:16,850 --> 00:25:22,550
That's right. I have no reason to eat chicken feet or go to our hideout when you are not here.

286
00:25:34,300 --> 00:25:36,960
I think I am getting old.

287
00:25:36,960 --> 00:25:41,140
You just realized that? That's nothing new.

288
00:25:41,140 --> 00:25:43,760
I used to like my heart fluttering

289
00:25:43,760 --> 00:25:48,560
so much so I couldn't see anything else.

290
00:25:49,700 --> 00:25:53,660
But now, that's too heavy for me.

291
00:25:54,800 --> 00:25:58,720
I think I am at the right age to have my heart dulled.

292
00:25:58,720 --> 00:26:01,560
But it isn't easy.

293
00:26:01,560 --> 00:26:04,530
Having your heart fluttering is a good thing.

294
00:26:04,530 --> 00:26:08,490
That's how you get to have blinders on and keep marching on.

295
00:26:08,490 --> 00:26:10,970
I need to control my breathing.

296
00:26:12,200 --> 00:26:14,590
Are you worried that you might fail?

297
00:26:14,590 --> 00:26:17,950
No! Of course not.

298
00:26:18,800 --> 00:26:22,350
Then be just like Oh Ha Na and push on until the end.

299
00:26:31,400 --> 00:26:35,350
You really haven't gone to our hideout once? Why didn't you clean up at least?

300
00:26:35,350 --> 00:26:37,720
I have been busy, too.

301
00:26:37,720 --> 00:26:40,200
Let's run!

302
00:27:01,200 --> 00:27:03,430
Alright.

303
00:27:04,800 --> 00:27:09,280
- Ah the smell...It's so good.
- Tada.

304
00:27:09,280 --> 00:27:10,970
Wow.

305
00:27:10,970 --> 00:27:14,720
I ate this during the local stay and it is awesome.

306
00:27:14,720 --> 00:27:18,160
You'll gain weight eating things like this at night.

307
00:27:18,160 --> 00:27:21,140
I am at the age. Unless I fill my insides

308
00:27:21,140 --> 00:27:25,060
I can't sleep very well.

309
00:27:27,300 --> 00:27:29,560
Here.

310
00:27:36,800 --> 00:27:38,150
This is too delicious.

311
00:27:38,150 --> 00:27:39,990
Isn't it?

312
00:27:40,900 --> 00:27:42,690
So, how is 'becoming a fan' going?

313
00:27:42,690 --> 00:27:46,180
Oh, classical music is too difficult.

314
00:27:46,900 --> 00:27:50,780
Hey! Shouldn't you be dating as well?

315
00:27:51,900 --> 00:27:53,260
I should.

316
00:27:53,260 --> 00:27:57,740
Although it wasn't that you can't date, but won't date.

317
00:27:59,700 --> 00:28:05,540
You suppressing your feelings and taking a month long trip and being friends again when you got back.

318
00:28:05,540 --> 00:28:07,940
How is it that easy for you?

319
00:28:10,700 --> 00:28:12,840
Does it seem easy to you?

320
00:28:15,500 --> 00:28:19,180
It's not easy. I am just doing my best to do it.

321
00:28:30,100 --> 00:28:31,760
This is good.

322
00:28:40,500 --> 00:28:42,830
When will you be back from your business trip?

323
00:28:42,830 --> 00:28:45,330
Tomorrow afternoon. I'll be back.

324
00:28:45,330 --> 00:28:48,070
Okay. Be sure to eat!

325
00:28:48,070 --> 00:28:50,650
Okay.

326
00:29:04,500 --> 00:29:08,680
Is my Noona by any chance taking a business trip with Cha Seo Hoo?

327
00:29:08,680 --> 00:29:11,750
How did you know that?

328
00:29:15,400 --> 00:29:18,970
Why are you so interested in Cha Seo Hoo?

329
00:29:18,970 --> 00:29:23,170
I have a lot of interest in my Noona's business.

330
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:27,610
And being the first-born son, I have to take care of things without exception.

331
00:29:29,300 --> 00:29:31,960
You are really admirable.

332
00:29:34,500 --> 00:29:38,060
I would be better than anyone, if not only for Hyung Won.

333
00:29:38,060 --> 00:29:39,780
What?

334
00:29:46,300 --> 00:29:48,310
I really hate getting into fights.

335
00:29:48,310 --> 00:29:49,670
Did you fight with your girlfriend again?

336
00:29:49,670 --> 00:29:53,550
She said I forgot some special day but she won't say what it is.

337
00:29:53,550 --> 00:29:56,270
How does she have so many special days?

338
00:29:56,270 --> 00:29:58,980
Must be nice to have so many special days.

339
00:29:58,980 --> 00:30:03,720
Since you are off today, any plan for a date?

340
00:30:03,720 --> 00:30:06,180
I wish...

341
00:30:07,200 --> 00:30:10,440
Pianist Park Jong Hoon's Very Special Liszt Recital

342
00:30:28,900 --> 00:30:31,630
Your name is...

343
00:30:33,500 --> 00:30:36,390
Choi...

344
00:30:36,390 --> 00:30:40,010
Didn't know you'd prefer my music, Ajumoni?

345
00:30:41,500 --> 00:30:42,390
Huh?

346
00:30:42,390 --> 00:30:45,030
You didn't go to the public bathhouse today?

347
00:31:00,300 --> 00:31:02,340
Ahjussi!

348
00:31:03,600 --> 00:31:04,590
Ahjussi?

349
00:31:04,590 --> 00:31:06,550
You are not apologizing properly?

350
00:31:06,550 --> 00:31:08,970
You'd ruin my day! So early in the morning...

351
00:31:12,200 --> 00:31:15,000
I am sorry, Ahjumma.

352
00:31:16,100 --> 00:31:20,940
Omo, what? Was that an apology?

353
00:31:20,940 --> 00:31:25,450
Hey! Ugh, seriously!

354
00:31:30,800 --> 00:31:33,420
Omo, omo!

355
00:31:34,400 --> 00:31:35,720
Are you not going?

356
00:31:35,720 --> 00:31:38,400
Oh, my God. Omo!

357
00:31:43,190 --> 00:31:44,920
- Take your seat.
- Ah, thank you.

358
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:47,520
Hello.

359
00:31:54,340 --> 00:31:56,420
Hello.

360
00:32:06,970 --> 00:32:08,970
Hello.

361
00:32:10,300 --> 00:32:15,650
♬ There is no reason to love you ♬

362
00:32:16,970 --> 00:32:22,360
♬ But I didn't know that ♬

363
00:32:24,140 --> 00:32:30,890
Excuse me.
♬ You, so blinding a person ♬

364
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:37,760
♬ Were definitely there beside me ♬

365
00:32:37,800 --> 00:32:43,430
♬ Was it always warm ♬

366
00:32:44,620 --> 00:32:50,150
♬ With you as the only one for me ♬

367
00:32:51,460 --> 00:32:54,970
♬ Is it okay to laugh about it ♬

368
00:32:54,970 --> 00:32:58,290
♬ The hard days past ♬

369
00:32:58,290 --> 00:33:04,320
♬ Because you were always there ♬

370
00:33:04,320 --> 00:33:11,140
♬ Even my heart didn't know how I felt ♬

371
00:33:11,140 --> 00:33:18,010
♬ Perhaps because you were always beside me ♬

372
00:33:18,010 --> 00:33:25,730
♬ From when it was
Or how it started ♬

373
00:33:25,730 --> 00:33:35,740
♬ Neither you nor I were aware ♬

374
00:34:23,100 --> 00:34:27,490
Gather your friends together! Let's have a meal together.

375
00:34:29,880 --> 00:34:32,270
- My friends?
- Hm.

376
00:34:32,270 --> 00:34:34,260
Call Choi Won too.

377
00:34:35,740 --> 00:34:41,300
People around me need some time to accept you.

378
00:34:44,010 --> 00:34:48,210
At your friend's wedding too... What is the problem?

379
00:34:48,210 --> 00:34:51,680
I love you Seo Hoo, but...

380
00:34:51,680 --> 00:34:56,510
Don't think all the people around me will accept you.

381
00:34:57,310 --> 00:34:59,420
Am I someone who needs to be accepted?

382
00:34:59,420 --> 00:35:02,310
Then why do you want to see my friends?

383
00:35:02,310 --> 00:35:07,830
Because I want to know all about your work and the people associated with you.

384
00:35:07,830 --> 00:35:09,520
That is your method.

385
00:35:09,520 --> 00:35:13,010
Whatever it is, I am trying for you.

386
00:35:13,010 --> 00:35:15,960
Then try waiting too.

387
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:18,600
I am a different person the from the one you used to date.

388
00:35:18,600 --> 00:35:23,490
I hope you would be different from before too.

389
00:35:26,630 --> 00:35:28,150
Okay.

390
00:35:50,650 --> 00:35:52,180
- Mom!
- Ha Na!

391
00:35:52,180 --> 00:35:53,620
Mom!

392
00:35:53,620 --> 00:35:55,540
You came.

393
00:36:02,570 --> 00:36:04,300
Have you been well?

394
00:36:06,290 --> 00:36:08,360
Mom...

395
00:36:08,360 --> 00:36:10,590
Seo Hoo, I'm sorry.

396
00:36:13,030 --> 00:36:14,970
I'll call you back later.

397
00:36:23,410 --> 00:36:27,920
Seriously, Noona, you should have known this would happen when you two were going to work together.

398
00:36:27,920 --> 00:36:29,610
Shut up.

399
00:36:30,850 --> 00:36:32,520
Ha Na, you...!

400
00:36:34,100 --> 00:36:36,170
What's happening?

401
00:36:38,940 --> 00:36:43,500
I am seeing Cha Seo Hoo again.

402
00:36:43,500 --> 00:36:48,780
What? I've been letting you do whatever you want, but what now? Are you in your right mind or not?

403
00:36:48,780 --> 00:36:50,870
Honey.

404
00:36:54,150 --> 00:36:56,960
Honey!

405
00:36:58,140 --> 00:36:59,930
Mom!

406
00:36:59,930 --> 00:37:03,270
What are you thinking, seeing that bastard again?

407
00:37:03,270 --> 00:37:09,690
Mom... I... decided to trust him again.

408
00:37:13,290 --> 00:37:16,080
This girl! How come you're acting like this?

409
00:37:16,080 --> 00:37:17,870
When was it that you were crying your heart out?

410
00:37:17,870 --> 00:37:20,950
Seo Hoo is really trying too.

411
00:37:20,950 --> 00:37:24,390
I really will do better this time.

412
00:37:27,090 --> 00:37:29,510
This is serious.

413
00:37:31,520 --> 00:37:34,010
Hey! Why is that there?

414
00:37:34,010 --> 00:37:37,100
Uh, this. It was thrown away in front of our house so I brought it in.

415
00:37:37,100 --> 00:37:38,880
What about this?

416
00:37:40,460 --> 00:37:42,440
That bastard gave you this?

417
00:37:45,930 --> 00:37:48,520
This moron!

418
00:37:48,520 --> 00:37:50,930
Because you brought this in

419
00:37:50,930 --> 00:37:53,170
you put that bastard next to your Noona!

420
00:37:53,170 --> 00:37:55,060
Why are you blaming me?

421
00:37:55,060 --> 00:37:58,170
Hey! I don't know!

422
00:38:06,600 --> 00:38:08,130
Choi Won!

423
00:38:15,670 --> 00:38:19,500
Let's not get too close like meeting twice a day.

424
00:38:20,630 --> 00:38:22,450
I am on my way back after taking Ha Na home.

425
00:38:22,450 --> 00:38:24,460
Then continue with your path.

426
00:38:24,460 --> 00:38:26,760
We need to be friends.

427
00:38:30,660 --> 00:38:32,890
Don't you know about friends?

428
00:38:33,560 --> 00:38:37,230
Like friends between you and Oh Ha Na. Friends.

429
00:38:37,230 --> 00:38:38,780
You must be crazy.

430
00:38:39,530 --> 00:38:42,860
You and Ha Na have been so close.

431
00:38:42,860 --> 00:38:44,220
Let me in there too.

432
00:38:44,220 --> 00:38:46,440
You really are only thinking about yourself.

433
00:38:46,440 --> 00:38:50,460
Don't make me a third person in Ha Na's matter.

434
00:38:51,640 --> 00:38:55,580
I have no interest in your relationship with Ha Na.

435
00:39:08,050 --> 00:39:09,640
Father.

436
00:39:09,640 --> 00:39:11,240
You came?

437
00:39:11,240 --> 00:39:12,620
Yes.

438
00:39:13,630 --> 00:39:15,450
What's the occasion?

439
00:39:18,670 --> 00:39:22,650
Won! Did you know about it?

440
00:39:23,280 --> 00:39:25,460
About what?

441
00:39:25,460 --> 00:39:29,170
Ha Na is seeing that guy  Cha Seo Hoo again.

442
00:39:30,090 --> 00:39:32,260
You knew about it, didn't you?

443
00:39:34,210 --> 00:39:37,280
Yes. I knew about it.

444
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:40,270
Then you should have told me.

445
00:39:40,270 --> 00:39:42,730
Or you should have stopped Ha Na.

446
00:39:43,680 --> 00:39:45,380
I'm sorry.

447
00:39:46,500 --> 00:39:47,750
I...

448
00:39:50,930 --> 00:39:54,400
I am just so upset with Ha Na.

449
00:39:55,020 --> 00:39:58,670
I was just once disappointed in her.

450
00:39:58,670 --> 00:40:02,400
Without her parents' consent, she gathered all her friends.

451
00:40:02,400 --> 00:40:06,040
She wanted to have an engagement ceremony or exchange of vows. Whatever it was,

452
00:40:06,040 --> 00:40:09,340
she turned our household upside down. And as if that wasn't enough,

453
00:40:10,500 --> 00:40:16,180
she locked herself in her room for days, without eating, when she got back. Thinking about that,

454
00:40:17,830 --> 00:40:20,960
how can I watch her seeing that bastard again?

455
00:40:23,540 --> 00:40:28,020
It probably was a difficult decision Ha Na made.

456
00:40:28,020 --> 00:40:33,030
So why would she make that difficult choice again?

457
00:40:43,490 --> 00:40:47,690
You punk. Why didn't you stop her from the heartache?

458
00:40:47,690 --> 00:40:52,500
You and Ha Na were always stuck together.

459
00:40:52,500 --> 00:40:56,470
What were you doing that you couldn't even have Ha Na's heart?

460
00:40:57,540 --> 00:41:01,080
Uhh, these fools...

461
00:41:01,080 --> 00:41:02,790
Ha Na...

462
00:41:06,260 --> 00:41:08,310
Will be all right.

463
00:41:12,240 --> 00:41:14,320
She will be all right.

464
00:41:18,420 --> 00:41:20,160
You...

465
00:41:22,390 --> 00:41:25,130
don't come to our house from now on.

466
00:41:43,370 --> 00:41:50,360
Timing and Subtitles brought to you by The Timeless Lovers @ Viki

467
00:41:58,280 --> 00:42:00,140
[Cha Seo Hoo]
I love you.

468
00:42:34,600 --> 00:42:36,360
Dad.

469
00:42:39,180 --> 00:42:41,140
Have a seat.

470
00:42:53,460 --> 00:42:58,280
Until now, from time to time, I still

471
00:42:59,640 --> 00:43:04,200
remember a little girl saying she will marry her daddy,

472
00:43:04,200 --> 00:43:06,800
like it was yesterday.

473
00:43:09,020 --> 00:43:13,900
To me, a man of your choice,

474
00:43:13,900 --> 00:43:17,180
even if he is the best man in the world,

475
00:43:17,960 --> 00:43:20,200
giving you up would still feel like a loss.

476
00:43:23,980 --> 00:43:27,220
No matter how great a guy is,

477
00:43:27,220 --> 00:43:33,920
a man who'd make my daughter shed even one tear,

478
00:43:33,920 --> 00:43:36,820
would absolutely not be accepted.

479
00:43:40,720 --> 00:43:44,500
My daughter is the best one in the world.

480
00:43:50,900 --> 00:43:54,420
Dad, I am sorry.

481
00:43:58,180 --> 00:44:03,400
Your mom and dad can't hate you no matter what you do.

482
00:44:04,580 --> 00:44:08,560
What can we do? That's not something we are capable of.

483
00:44:10,500 --> 00:44:12,960
I did wrong.

484
00:44:14,480 --> 00:44:16,720
I will do better.

485
00:44:18,240 --> 00:44:22,560
Like your daughter, I will do better.

486
00:44:24,720 --> 00:44:27,060
I am sorry, Dad.

487
00:44:50,980 --> 00:44:53,300
You and Ha Na are always stuck together.

488
00:44:53,300 --> 00:44:57,540
What were you doing that you couldn't even have Ha Na's heart?

489
00:45:08,500 --> 00:45:11,580
You can accompany me this afternoon, right?

490
00:45:16,600 --> 00:45:18,820
This is my company!

491
00:45:18,820 --> 00:45:22,140
I know. Let's go.

492
00:45:22,140 --> 00:45:27,580
Look here. I am working right now and I have a lot of work to do.

493
00:45:27,580 --> 00:45:32,820
And a boyfriend is supposed to carry heavy things for his girlfriend when she is carrying it.

494
00:45:44,600 --> 00:45:47,000
Let's drive around at night.

495
00:45:47,000 --> 00:45:51,300
I still have some work to do, and today I shouldn't be late going home.

496
00:45:53,220 --> 00:45:55,060
Why?

497
00:45:57,620 --> 00:45:59,620
The atmosphere at home is a bit heavy.

498
00:46:02,500 --> 00:46:05,100
Is it because of me?

499
00:46:07,560 --> 00:46:10,100
Yes.

500
00:46:10,100 --> 00:46:13,120
Fine then. I  won't get you home too late.

501
00:46:18,920 --> 00:46:20,780
What?

502
00:46:22,720 --> 00:46:26,720
It's nothing.

503
00:46:33,180 --> 00:46:34,420
Yeah, Chang Soo.

504
00:46:34,420 --> 00:46:37,960
Today? I'm off today.

505
00:46:37,960 --> 00:46:40,260
In the evening?

506
00:46:40,260 --> 00:46:42,620
Okay, I'll see you there then.

507
00:46:57,760 --> 00:47:02,960
Shall we see how much you've advanced playing piano and not your work.

508
00:47:02,960 --> 00:47:06,120
I wasn't good at it then, so how could I be good now?

509
00:47:06,120 --> 00:47:08,800
Okay, well then just try hard from now on.

510
00:47:08,800 --> 00:47:12,620
If you want to take the world-renowned pianist around.

511
00:47:12,620 --> 00:47:14,980
Are you provoking my competitive side?

512
00:47:17,580 --> 00:47:19,840
You are right. I am provoking you.

513
00:47:34,540 --> 00:47:39,540
Ah, but really... I don't think I have a talent for it.

514
00:47:40,720 --> 00:47:42,340
What are you doing??

515
00:47:42,340 --> 00:47:44,760
Here. I am taking a photo.

516
00:47:46,500 --> 00:47:49,600
What's this, all of a sudden?

517
00:47:49,600 --> 00:47:51,300
- Show it to me.
- Nope.

518
00:47:51,300 --> 00:47:53,580
- Show me.
- No. It's nothing.

519
00:47:53,580 --> 00:47:55,660
- Later, later
- Let me see it. Let me see it.

520
00:47:55,660 --> 00:47:57,040
Here, here, here, here!

521
00:47:57,040 --> 00:47:59,020
And like this!

522
00:47:59,020 --> 00:48:02,580
is how you upload and reveal a couple picture.

523
00:48:04,540 --> 00:48:06,100
- Seo Hoo!
- Hm?

524
00:48:06,100 --> 00:48:09,700
- Why are doing this on your own?
- What?

525
00:48:09,700 --> 00:48:13,700
Calling before you come to my office is the right thing to do.

526
00:48:13,700 --> 00:48:18,460
Even uploading this kind of picture, you should ask me first.

527
00:48:18,460 --> 00:48:22,420
Is this something you should get upset about it?

528
00:48:22,420 --> 00:48:26,280
I tried to understand you no matter what you did before,

529
00:48:26,280 --> 00:48:30,280
whatever it was... Because I loved you,

530
00:48:30,280 --> 00:48:32,480
I just let it all go and thought it was okay.

531
00:48:32,480 --> 00:48:39,460
But now it's different. I wish you could be a bit more considerate of me.

532
00:48:43,860 --> 00:48:47,160
I am sorry. I will go first today.

533
00:48:50,260 --> 00:48:51,900
Ha Na!

534
00:49:00,900 --> 00:49:03,520
So did you have fun on your honeymoon?

535
00:49:03,520 --> 00:49:06,960
"Honeymoon baby." Making that was my goal.

536
00:49:06,960 --> 00:49:09,770
It's a pretty big dream.

537
00:49:11,400 --> 00:49:12,680
Right.

538
00:49:12,680 --> 00:49:18,280
I saw Ha Na's graduation photo while I was organizing my wedding photos.

539
00:49:18,280 --> 00:49:20,320
You guys are totally funny.

540
00:49:20,320 --> 00:49:24,090
How can you have two different graduation photos?

541
00:49:30,100 --> 00:49:31,820
There's another thing I want to do.

542
00:49:31,820 --> 00:49:33,640
What is it this time?

543
00:49:33,640 --> 00:49:36,480
From high school until college,

544
00:49:36,480 --> 00:49:41,000
I want to have our graduation photos in our graduation albums. What do you think?

545
00:49:41,000 --> 00:49:43,120
How are we going to graduate together?

546
00:49:43,120 --> 00:49:46,020
You'll graduate first while I am serving in the military.

547
00:49:47,760 --> 00:49:50,500
I think it will be good memories for us.

548
00:50:07,120 --> 00:50:09,020
KOREA!

549
00:50:14,300 --> 00:50:17,680
What's with your clothes?

550
00:50:17,680 --> 00:50:19,180
Uh...Seriously.

551
00:50:19,180 --> 00:50:23,600
I parachuted three times to be here. Don't be embarrassed.

552
00:50:23,600 --> 00:50:29,680
- Okay - I'm taking the picture now!
♬ I couldn't say no ♬

553
00:50:29,680 --> 00:50:35,080
♬  The more I ask my heart ♬

554
00:50:35,080 --> 00:50:39,340
♬ I will say what needs to be said  ♬

555
00:50:39,340 --> 00:50:43,000
Choi Won!

556
00:50:43,000 --> 00:50:46,600
Oh Ha Na!
♬ It's is a long and endless journey ♬

557
00:50:46,600 --> 00:50:49,200
Hey you.  Were you going to try to take the picture without me?

558
00:50:49,200 --> 00:50:52,300
♬  I am going toward you  ♬

559
00:50:52,300 --> 00:50:56,040
One, two.

560
00:50:56,040 --> 00:51:02,480
♬ Now I can't be stopped  ♬

561
00:51:02,480 --> 00:51:07,380
Yeah, that's right. We did do that, didn't we....
♬ Turn around and look at me ♬

562
00:51:07,380 --> 00:51:13,840
Yeah, seriously. You two are probably the only ones who have two college graduation photos.

563
00:51:19,820 --> 00:51:22,640
Seriously though,

564
00:51:22,640 --> 00:51:24,700
You shouldn't try to take broken things and fix them.

565
00:51:24,700 --> 00:51:27,440
It'll just break in the exact same way again.

566
00:51:27,440 --> 00:51:30,000
Seo Hoo and I are really doing just fine, and--

567
00:51:30,000 --> 00:51:32,700
So you are calling me after you had a fight?

568
00:51:32,700 --> 00:51:34,360
This is what I'm saying.

569
00:51:34,360 --> 00:51:37,660
- Be a bit*h.
- What?

570
00:51:37,660 --> 00:51:41,680
Don't get hurt this time. You hurt him first this time.

571
00:51:41,680 --> 00:51:44,260
I won't get hurt nor inflict pain on him.

572
00:51:44,260 --> 00:51:45,900
Is Cha Seo Hoo becoming Lee Seo Hoo?

573
00:51:45,900 --> 00:51:49,340
Old habits die hard, you know? People don't change.

574
00:51:49,340 --> 00:51:52,120
You guys are so great.

575
00:51:52,120 --> 00:51:54,400
Can't I at least have you on my side?

576
00:51:54,400 --> 00:51:57,240
You live life alone.

577
00:51:57,240 --> 00:51:59,240
I need a cheerleading squad.

578
00:51:59,240 --> 00:52:02,820
You are the one who kicked your own luck away.

579
00:52:02,820 --> 00:52:06,360
You mean bit*h. Hey, hang up!

580
00:52:28,380 --> 00:52:33,880
♬ There's nothing special about today. ♬

581
00:52:33,880 --> 00:52:39,680
♬ While except for me ♬

582
00:52:39,680 --> 00:52:44,660
♬ Everyone seems happy ♬

583
00:52:44,660 --> 00:52:48,500
The picture looks good. Would you like to hang out tomorrow?

584
00:52:50,920 --> 00:52:56,020
♬ Looking in a mirror without focusing ♬

585
00:52:56,100 --> 00:53:01,900
♬ When our eyes meet ♬
I want to see you.

586
00:53:01,960 --> 00:53:09,360
♬ Like someone shining a light in my face ♬

587
00:53:10,120 --> 00:53:13,730
♬ You are blotted out by other thoughts ♬

588
00:53:13,730 --> 00:53:19,410
♬ Although for some still unexplainable ♬

589
00:53:19,410 --> 00:53:24,980
♬ Reason love emerges ♬

590
00:53:24,980 --> 00:53:31,030
♬ When like a habit the thought of you rises to the surface  ♬

591
00:53:31,030 --> 00:53:35,660
♬ That's exactly my song of love  ♬

592
00:53:35,680 --> 00:53:37,390
But, what does that matter?

593
00:53:37,390 --> 00:53:39,190
I'm not afraid of being completely injured.

594
00:53:40,360 --> 00:53:42,640
I''m still living life to its fullest, beautifully.

595
00:53:43,830 --> 00:53:48,390
Marketing focusing on sensitivity is currently ongoing on Jumei and ChaAndy's agreed concept.

596
00:53:48,390 --> 00:53:54,100
As a result of the recent meeting, Jumei has shown positive interest in collaborating with the ChaAndy Project.

597
00:53:54,100 --> 00:53:58,520
Excuse me, Jumei has just contacted us.

598
00:54:26,520 --> 00:54:28,290
Mom!

599
00:54:29,350 --> 00:54:33,740
Mom, are you okay?

600
00:54:48,870 --> 00:54:52,550
Team Leader Oh Ha Na will be solely responsible for this project.

601
00:54:52,550 --> 00:54:57,140
They want Team Leader Oh to be in charge of it, so what can we do?

602
00:54:57,150 --> 00:55:01,130
It seems that Team Leader Oh Ha Na will also know better than anyone else what they want.

603
00:55:01,170 --> 00:55:03,230
Yes, I understand.

604
00:55:03,230 --> 00:55:07,530
You must have been really determined on this business trip to China.

605
00:55:17,530 --> 00:55:22,660
Please check up on the things that I have been unable to follow up on.

606
00:55:34,550 --> 00:55:38,910
Ah, Mother! How did this happen? Where and how much are you hurt?

607
00:55:38,910 --> 00:55:40,990
Aren't you going to the hospital?

608
00:55:40,990 --> 00:55:44,650
She won't go, saying she's fine, even though she can't even move.

609
00:55:45,690 --> 00:55:48,860
Why did you even go so far as to call Won?

610
00:55:48,860 --> 00:55:52,970
Well, what else was I supposed to do? I wasn't able to get a hold of anyone else.

611
00:55:53,010 --> 00:55:55,610
Oh let go. Move over. I need to clean.

612
00:55:55,610 --> 00:55:58,770
Just lie down.

613
00:56:11,180 --> 00:56:12,310
Yeah, Seo Hoo?

614
00:56:12,310 --> 00:56:14,070
Why weren't you picking up your phone?

615
00:56:14,070 --> 00:56:17,320
Just compliment me and tell me I did well regardless.

616
00:56:17,320 --> 00:56:18,790
What is it?

617
00:56:18,790 --> 00:56:22,360
Our company decided to push forward in working with Jumei.

618
00:56:22,360 --> 00:56:26,230
What? So it was good that I went on the business trip with you?

619
00:56:26,230 --> 00:56:27,780
That's great.

620
00:56:27,780 --> 00:56:30,160
Shall we meet up tonight?

621
00:56:31,100 --> 00:56:33,020
I am getting another call.

622
00:56:33,020 --> 00:56:35,570
- I'll call you back right away!
- Okay.

623
00:56:36,990 --> 00:56:38,570
Yeah, Dae Bok.

624
00:56:39,550 --> 00:56:43,350
What? Mom? How badly?

625
00:56:43,350 --> 00:56:46,020
I got it. I'll go back quickly.

626
00:56:51,190 --> 00:56:56,450
I'm sorry, Seo Hoo. I think I need to return home quickly today.

627
00:57:48,010 --> 00:57:51,130
Mom, are you okay?  Did you get hurt badly?

628
00:57:51,130 --> 00:57:54,050
No, no. I'm fine.

629
00:57:55,330 --> 00:57:59,720
- What about dinner?
- Sit, let's eat together.

630
00:58:02,070 --> 00:58:06,130
Won worked really hard today.

631
00:58:06,130 --> 00:58:08,620
It was nothing.

632
00:58:19,650 --> 00:58:22,540
It's a relief that she wasn't hurt too badly.

633
00:58:23,370 --> 00:58:25,230
Thanks.

634
00:58:27,000 --> 00:58:30,670
I'm going to have a beer so go on home.

635
00:58:30,670 --> 00:58:33,520
- Oh, okay.
- Yes.

636
00:58:44,070 --> 00:58:46,560
Oh Ha Na.

637
00:58:50,460 --> 00:58:51,860
Yeah?

638
00:59:13,530 --> 00:59:15,230
You keep it!

639
00:59:16,500 --> 00:59:20,340
That saved me many times during my trip.

640
00:59:22,400 --> 00:59:26,900
It is pretty effective for calling for help.

641
00:59:34,080 --> 00:59:36,420
It sounds great!

642
01:00:16,460 --> 01:00:25,920
Timing and Subtitles brought to you by The Timeless Lovers @ Viki

643
01:00:35,540 --> 01:00:37,900
How did you come here?

644
01:00:37,900 --> 01:00:40,390
Isn't today your departure day?

645
01:00:40,390 --> 01:00:44,510
My training can't be more important than you in my life.

646
01:00:46,950 --> 01:00:50,960
Are you going to ask me to take care of you after you get fired?

647
01:00:50,960 --> 01:00:55,830
Hey! Is this something you should say to a friend who gave up on Paris to come see you?

648
01:00:57,330 --> 01:01:00,100
My wasted Paris...

649
01:01:00,120 --> 01:01:03,200
They will give me another chance later, right?

650
01:01:06,890 --> 01:01:10,100
When I get my first paycheck, I will buy you a ticket to Paris.

651
01:01:10,100 --> 01:01:12,730
This is for real. You promised.

652
01:01:12,730 --> 01:01:18,110
Of course. But didn't you say you'd have to wait another three years if you don't go this time?

653
01:01:18,110 --> 01:01:22,100
Delaying three years won't change my life, will it?

654
01:01:22,100 --> 01:01:24,560
Right. Will it change?

655
01:01:24,560 --> 01:01:27,860
The choices we made in order to stay together.

656
01:01:27,860 --> 01:01:32,400
And those choices we made are the reasons why we can't be together now.

657
01:01:32,400 --> 01:01:35,880
Of course we didn't know then.

658
01:01:35,880 --> 01:01:40,450
♬ Why am I feeling like this? It doesn't make sense. ♬

659
01:01:40,450 --> 01:01:45,480
♬ Are your shining eyes looking at me love? ♬

660
01:01:45,480 --> 01:01:50,650
♬ Shall I try to tell you once now?♬

661
01:01:50,650 --> 01:01:54,600
♬ Shall we try to start our love? ♬

662
01:01:54,600 --> 01:01:57,600
♬ Why are we like this? ♬

663
01:01:57,600 --> 01:02:01,150
Keep playing house and stay as friends.

664
01:02:01,150 --> 01:02:04,770
Just get married when you get older.

665
01:02:04,770 --> 01:02:06,220
Shall I?

666
01:02:07,370 --> 01:02:09,240
Take it and when you think of something, come back.

667
01:02:09,240 --> 01:02:13,710
What do I have to try to remember? The memory of us loving each other? The memory of you hurting me?

668
01:02:13,710 --> 01:02:17,530
Or the memory of you being totally fine after hurting me?

669
01:02:17,590 --> 01:02:20,630
What do you think we can do with those memories?

670
01:02:20,630 --> 01:02:22,650
I'm not going for the overseas training.

671
01:02:23,600 --> 01:02:26,260
What's the reason now?

672
01:02:26,260 --> 01:02:28,340
I think my opportunity is here.

673
01:02:28,340 --> 01:02:31,610
I'm sorry for not being able to be on your side.
